|C                                     |-- DOC concentration, kg/m[.sup]3[/]| 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|C[.sub]f[/]                         |-- BOD concentration in feed, kg-BOD/-| 
|                                      |m[.sup]3[/]                         | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|C[.sub]p[/]                         |-- DOC concentration in membrane perm-| 
|                                      |eate, kg/m[.sup]3[/]                | 
