  1. N. Kanekuni, Chemical Engineering (Tokyo), Vol. 36, No. 
11, pp 50-55 (1991). 
  2. H. Masuda and N. Ohkuma, Chemical Engineering (Tokyo), 
Vol. 36, No. 11, pp 62-69 (1991). 

