                               ZnO                      3.2                      1.2 

                               SiO[.sub]2[/]             2.3                      1.0 

Sludge          appearance     color                    brown powder             black powder 
accompanying 
with 
pretreated 
water 

                analysis       av. diameter             3 Êm                     10 Êm 

                               form                     amorphous iron oxide     mixture of Fe[.sub]2[/] 
                                                                                 O[.sub]3[/] and 
                                                                                 Fe[.sub]3[/]O[.sub]4[/] 

                               Total CN                 185 mg/kg                &lt;1 mg/kg 

                composition    Fe                       37.0                     61.0 
                wt% 

